description:
Use this app and be proficient in swimming.
 • Swimming is the, one of the best exercise for muscles of the chest, arms and core development.
• If you're very serious about increasing your strength or are you beginner in swimming or are you preparing any swimming competition then this app is designed for you!!!
• Swimming is very important exercise for weight loss.
• In this application there will be a predefined 4 week program, so you no need to remember schedule.
• Rest timer is also defined in this application, so no need to use/run stop watch.
• Once completed the total activity this application will save the log for feature reference.
• You can delete or reset logs at any point of time.
• This application will allow you can change the schedule, and vibration.
• This application will add the logs for feature reference.
• If you are strictly following the training program definitely you will be a proficient in swimming and you can also participate in any events also.
• You can definitely you will gain strength using this application & performing the training program.

Features: 
• Ideal app for gaining the strength. 
• Predefined 4 week program, so you no need to remember schedule. 
• Predefined timer is defined in this application so no need to use stop watch also.
• Auto saving logs for feature reference.
• You can also reset the logs or deleting the logs at any point of time.
